Taunton.Fuller-Dauphin Estate:
Fuller-Dauphin Estate, is a historic house and former estate known as "The Maples" located at 145 School Street in Taunton, Massachusetts.
It was built in 1872 for local Judge William Eddy Fuller and designed by local architect E.C. Chandler. It is a 2-1/2 story central hall plan Italianate style house with spacious proportions and disciplined ornament.
